oakcurric:unit-2597
  a curric:Unit ;
  rdfs:label "The concerto through time"@en ;
  curric:slug "the-concerto-through-time" ;
  rdfs:comment """This unit explores the development of the concerto through the Baroque, Classical
  and Romantic periods. Lessons focus on typical features and how these evolved in relation
  to stylistic trends during those periods. It also includes analysis of a series of case
  studies, exemplifying the developments."""@en ;
  curric:whyThisWhyNow "[TO BE ADDED]" ;
